Players guess a random WC 2026 player in up to 6 attempts. Each
wrong guess reveals 5 color-coded hints (nation/confederation,
position group, league, club, rating direction). Unlimited replays;
ranking tracks each user's best score (60→10 pts by attempts).
Saves to new `footle_scores` Supabase table.

https://claude.ai/code/session_01JoUbx78eQyJfz4RsysaGkr
