Replace full-nation filter with exact squad names sourced from official
announcements. Removes retired/uncalled players (Griezmann, Benzema,
Di Maria, Foden, Palmer, Savinho…) and injured/absent ones (Timber,
Balerdi). Pool: France 18, Spain 18, England 17, Brazil 17,
Netherlands 17, Belgium 17, Portugal 22, Argentina 19, Germany 16,
Uruguay 14.

https://claude.ai/code/session_01JoUbx78eQyJfz4RsysaGkr
